social_posts.post_text: Web3 IRL 🤘

What a Birthday weekend 🤘

After 6 months of recovering from hip surgery, the best gift I could’ve gotten was to be able to compete at the highest level in the sport I love the most & not knowing if I’d be able to physically/mentally get back to where I was 🙏 

The niche sport of Paddleball has provided me with some of life’s most fulfilling milestones. Continuing the family legacy is something I’m extremely proud of. 

1️⃣ Mixed Doubles Champions with ma girl 🏆 @aridanielle27 

2️⃣ Quarter Finals with the one and only @mike_dtv_ who flew up from Florida just to play with some kid he didn’t know too well 🙏 Gotcha

Another successful AF Pro Series Tournament of Champions event. Thank you again to the peeps in charge, and sponsors.

📸: @paddleballunited @ariellescarcella2 & MikeDTV

Always wanted to cover and continue the legendary backstage candid camera version of @stevienicks ‘Wild Heart’ 🙏

A completely different version of this song was released at a later time, leaving the OG version never to be fully heard 😮

So I decided to pay tribute to this lost version with @kariselle and tried to capture/continue what I always believed should’ve been the songs direction 🤘

Watch full version & vid in bio ⬆️

Story time: I met this dude @greggsgar back in 2020, he was the first vocalist/songwriter I ever worked with. We made a song together called “Far From Home” that totally changed our lives after going number 1 on radio (thank you so much @geronimobpm and @ridanaser ). Over the years we’ve become such close friends, but never got to play it out live together. A few weeks ago in NYC we finally got to drop it, mashed up with Above & Beyond’s “Prelude” and it blew the roof off the place. Love you brother @greggsgar let’s make another soon eh? 💙
📸 @paxton_loves_u
